# Giventa Layout Separation

## Public marketing (Globex)
- Routes: `/`, `/about-us`, `/services`, `/contact-us`, `/home`
- Shell: `src/app/(site)/layout.tsx` — GlobexHeader, GlobexFooter, GlobexInfoSidebar
- **Do not** add MOSC/Syro routes or `/mosc-redesign` to this project

## Admin + auth + API (mosc-temp backend pattern)
- Routes: `/admin/*`, `/sign-in`, `/sign-up`, `/api/*`, `/pages/api/proxy/*`
- **Outside** `(site)` route group — no Globex header/footer
- Clerk: satellite `www.giventa.com` → primary `www.event-site-manager.com`
- Admin link: `GlobexAdminLink` in header (client check via `/api/auth/admin-status`)

## Clerk satellite (giventa)
- Env: `NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_IS_SATELLITE=true`, absolute `NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=https://www.event-site-manager.com/sign-in`
- Config helpers: `src/lib/clerkSatellite.ts` → `getClerkSatelliteMiddlewareOptions()`, `getClerkProviderSatelliteProps()`
- See also: `clerk_auth_satellite_v7_handshake.mdc`, `clerk_auth_admin_user_lookup_avatar.mdc`
